content.rendered:
Directed by Sagar Ballary

Written by Dipankar Giri. Diane Charles. Diane Charles. Yashodhan Kelkar. Shubhodeep Pal

Star Abhay Deol (Rudra). Emily Shah (Roshni Thakkar (as Emily Anila Shah)). Steve Aldis (Plane Passenger). Rhys ap William (Mark). Sherry Baines (Nicola Bennett). Richard Elfyn (Richard Bennett). Julian Lewis Jones (Dale Bright). Joynal . Atul Kumar (Dr. Achyuta Samanta). Ross O’Hennessy (Tim Harris). Saujas Pannigrahy (Rugby Player). Stewart Wright (Paul Walsh)

Language English

Producers Preeti Bal. Shabbir Boxwala. Rubeena Dode. Jessica Kaur. Emily Shah. Prashant Shah. Azim Shaikh. Jaswant Singh

Production Bollywood Hollywood Production
